						<div class="postbody">Monitors are hard to film unless you are perfectly synchronized.  Either they synchronized perfectly to the monitor's refresh rate, or they overlaid a video afterwards.<br />Usually in commercials and film, screens are simulated because they are so hard to film well.</div>

					
